com.microsoft.azure.eventhubs

Interface PartitionReceiveHandler


  • public interface PartitionReceiveHandler
    The handler to invoke after receiving EventDatas from Microsoft Azure EventHubs. Use any implementation of this abstract class to specify user action when using PartitionReceiver's setReceiveHandler().
    See Also:
    PartitionReceiver.setReceiveHandler(com.microsoft.azure.eventhubs.PartitionReceiveHandler)

    • Method Detail

      • getMaxEventCount

        int getMaxEventCount()
        Maximum number of EventData to supply while invoking onReceive(Iterable)

        Ensure that the value should be less than or equal to the value of ReceiverOptions.getPrefetchCount()

        Returns:
        value indicating the maximum number of EventData to supply while invoking onReceive(Iterable)

      • onReceive

        void onReceive(Iterable<EventData> events)

      • onError
